<lyrics>[V1]
 1- nạs ktyr ʿly̱ ạsmk whm jạhlynk
 wnạs ạ̉ktr bạlạsm lk wbtʿbd gẖyrk
 wnạs tạnyyn tsẖtạq lk wttmny̱ tyjy lk
 wnạs hnạ wʿạysẖyn lk wtmwt wlạ thynk
 ạlqrạr- ạ̉h ạ̉h ạ̉h wʿạyzynk
 ạ̉h ạ̉h ạ̉h wḥạbynk
 tyjy bldnạ tạny wtzwr bldnạ tạny
 tyjy bldnạ tạny tyjy bywtnạ tạny
 bạlrwḥ bạ̹njylk bạlrwḥ bqy̱ nyjy lk
 2- nạs wạẓbwạ fy knạyshm wạnt gẖạyb ʿnhm
 wnạs kẖdmwạ fy knạyshm tʿạlymhm wʿlmhm
 wạlrwḥ byḍm ywmạty fy knystk mn gẖyrhm
 wnạs ʿmdạn wḥjạrẗ wmnạrẗ ạ̹ymạnhm
 3- nsẖhd hnạ ʿn ạ̉smk wạnt sẖạhd ʿnạ
 nḥml bfrḥ nyrk wạnt ạlly sẖạylnạ
 nkẖdm hnạ fy wlạdk wbtkẖdm fynạ
 nḥmy ạ̹ymạn ạ̹njylk wạ̹nt ạlly ḥạmynạ</lyrics>
